          "steps": [
            "Apply the Pythagorean theorem: a² + b² = c²",
            "Substitute values: 3² + 4² = c²",
            "Calculate: 9 + 16 = c²",
            "Simplify: 25 = c²",
            "Take square root: c = 5"
